  <brief_title>Triage Liaison Physician - Evaluation of a Novel Approach to Address Emergency Department Overcrowding</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of a Liaison Physician at the Triage Desk to Reduce Emergency Department Overcrowding and Improve Patient Flow.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Alberta</agency>
